2004-10-05 21:10  cpb

	* Makefile.PL (1.6), htmltopalmdoc (1.3), mobisucks (1.5):

	use HTML::Entities to attempt to handle HTML character entities.
	Unfortunately, HTML::Entities can't handle anything that isn't represented
	in 8859-1 so there's a little left over. We manually convert the stuff that
	we know about (mostly quotes) and strip out the rest.

